Events.Text: Hello I'd like to schedule a viewing of the apartment.

Scenario.UserTask: You are interested in viewing an apartment. Please schedule a viewing at One on Center Apartments for Tuesday at 5 pm. Your name is Angela. You have paid the application fee. Please include the following message with your booking request: I am particularly interested in the two bedroom units. If not, the studio is also fine.
Scenario.WizardTask: Help the user schedule an apartment viewing.
